Contacts - a CLI tool for managing Contacts

Usage: contacts <command> <args>

Commands:
    search <term>             searches all contacts and returns ones that match your query
    export <file.vcf>         path to export contacts to (.vcf file)
    import <file.vcf>         path to import contacts from
    list                      lists all contacts

Arguments:
    --help                      shows this message
    --db <path to db>           path to database directory (default is HOME/.contactsdir)